HEADWORD: Calvatia
<hw>Calvatia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus of puffballs having outer
casings whose upper parts break at maturity into angular pieces to
expose the spores.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Calvatia</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
